WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 3=

00:02:02.700 --> 00:02:06.500 line:80%
(Pillar of Righteousness)

00:02:34.540 --> 00:02:37.180 line:80%
(Pillar of Righteousness)

00:02:42.460 --> 00:02:44.140 line:80%
You wouldn't leave me

00:02:45.210 --> 00:02:48.020 line:80%
just to lure me to find
Yin Dai's handbook, right?

00:02:49.490 --> 00:02:50.750 line:80%
What exactly is in the handbook?

00:02:50.836 --> 00:02:52.550 line:80%
I just want to help you
uncover the truth.

00:02:53.690 --> 00:02:54.740 line:80%
Why don't you trust me?

00:02:56.759 --> 00:02:58.105 line:80%
I'll report to Master immediately.

00:02:58.560 --> 00:02:59.650 line:80%
I'm looking for the handbook

00:02:59.650 --> 00:03:00.970 line:80%
to avenge my father.

00:03:02.900 --> 00:03:03.820 line:80%
What does your revenge

00:03:03.970 --> 00:03:05.620 line:80%
have to do with Yin Dai's handbook?

00:03:08.530 --> 00:03:09.690 line:80%
It's said that the handbook

00:03:09.860 --> 00:03:11.620 line:80%
records the Disintegration,
a secret skill

00:03:11.780 --> 00:03:13.180 line:80%
passed down through generations

00:03:13.740 --> 00:03:15.020 line:80%
of Qingque lords.

00:03:15.930 --> 00:03:17.410 line:80%
Disintegration?

00:03:21.180 --> 00:03:22.020 line:80%
Rumor has it

00:03:23.020 --> 00:03:24.060 line:80%
that Nie Hengcheng

00:03:25.210 --> 00:03:26.810 line:80%
died from this technique.

00:03:27.650 --> 00:03:28.810 line:80%
If I can master it,

00:03:29.530 --> 00:03:30.780 line:80%
I'll surely avenge my father.

00:03:36.620 --> 00:03:38.210 line:80%
You fabricated a name

00:03:38.210 --> 00:03:39.690 line:80%
and tried to deceive me.

00:03:42.180 --> 00:03:43.970 line:80%
You've mostly recovered.

00:03:45.020 --> 00:03:47.090 line:80%
Move out tomorrow.

00:04:01.060 --> 00:04:02.060 line:80%
Disintegration

00:04:02.740 --> 00:04:04.780 line:80%
was created by Founder Beichen.

00:04:05.140 --> 00:04:06.340 line:80%
It can instantly boost power

00:04:06.780 --> 00:04:07.740 line:80%
and make one invincible.

00:04:09.900 --> 00:04:11.210 line:80%
Though formidable,

00:04:12.780 --> 00:04:14.490 line:80%
it'll backfire on the user.

00:04:14.490 --> 00:04:15.580 line:80%
(Young Cai Pingchun)

00:04:15.580 --> 00:04:16.780 line:80%
Meridians will collapse.

00:04:16.780 --> 00:04:17.650 line:80%
(Young Ning Xiaofeng)

00:04:17.650 --> 00:04:18.796 line:80%
Martial skills will be lost.

00:04:19.780 --> 00:04:20.620 line:80%
Ultimately,

00:04:21.210 --> 00:04:22.460 line:80%
the user will be dead.

00:04:25.410 --> 00:04:26.650 line:80%
Zhao, have you thought

00:04:27.380 --> 00:04:29.170 line:80%
why your aunt would practice this?

00:04:29.753 --> 00:04:30.833 line:80%
If nothing were suspicious,

00:04:31.446 --> 00:04:32.746 line:80%
why is Yin Dai's handbook missing

00:04:33.500 --> 00:04:35.380 line:80%
in the secret room?

00:04:50.290 --> 00:04:51.130 line:80%
Zhao.

00:04:51.940 --> 00:04:52.780 line:80%
Zhao?

00:04:54.580 --> 00:04:55.500 line:80%
Zhao,

00:04:56.260 --> 00:04:58.210 line:80%
do you think I'm very bad?

00:04:58.210 --> 00:04:59.500 line:80%
My effort has been in vain.

00:05:01.730 --> 00:05:02.570 line:80%
Xiaolan,

00:05:02.730 --> 00:05:03.820 line:80%
martial arts is like this.

00:05:04.460 --> 00:05:05.780 line:80%
At first, progress is slow.

00:05:06.970 --> 00:05:08.500 line:80%
You must be patient.

00:05:09.020 --> 00:05:09.860 line:80%
Later,

00:05:10.340 --> 00:05:11.970 line:80%
your power will grow steadily.

00:05:12.410 --> 00:05:13.380 line:80%
I'll go to Herb Hut later

00:05:13.380 --> 00:05:15.340 line:80%
to find some herbs
to strengthen your foundation.

00:05:15.380 --> 00:05:16.460 line:80%
Thanks, Zhao.

00:05:18.610 --> 00:05:20.730 line:80%
Though I can't be famous in Jianghu

00:05:21.170 --> 00:05:22.780 line:80%
at a young age and slay

00:05:23.050 --> 00:05:24.430 line:80%
the Chief of the demon sect alone

00:05:24.441 --> 00:05:25.210 line:80%
like Ms. Cai,

00:05:25.580 --> 00:05:27.500 line:80%
I'll take her as a role model

00:05:27.850 --> 00:05:28.690 line:80%
and never slack.

00:05:29.380 --> 00:05:30.940 line:80%
But she paid a heavy price.

00:05:35.290 --> 00:05:36.130 line:80%
The medicine for you.

00:05:38.340 --> 00:05:39.180 line:80%
Thanks, Uncle Lei.

00:05:41.850 --> 00:05:42.690 line:80%
Uncle Lei,

00:05:43.090 --> 00:05:46.050 line:80%
have you heard
of the Disintegration?

00:05:49.170 --> 00:05:50.010 line:80%
Who told you?

00:05:51.820 --> 00:05:53.340 line:80%
Will the user face

00:05:53.530 --> 00:05:55.170 line:80%
meridians collapse

00:05:55.170 --> 00:05:56.150 line:80%
and lose martial skills?

00:05:59.260 --> 00:06:00.730 line:80%
This fatal move

00:06:01.170 --> 00:06:02.260 line:80%
is forbidden.

00:06:03.340 --> 00:06:04.900 line:80%
Thus, successive Qingque lords

00:06:06.090 --> 00:06:07.650 line:80%
never taught it to outsiders.

00:06:08.826 --> 00:06:09.780 line:80%
Then why did Yin Dai...

00:06:09.780 --> 00:06:10.620 line:80%
Everyone is gone.

00:06:11.500 --> 00:06:12.580 line:80%
Why chase

00:06:13.140 --> 00:06:13.980 line:80%
old grudges?

00:06:17.256 --> 00:06:18.900 line:80%
This is a calming pouch for Chang Ning.

00:06:19.970 --> 00:06:20.810 line:80%
Take it back for him.

00:06:23.380 --> 00:06:24.220 line:80%
Yes.

00:06:42.900 --> 00:06:44.090 line:80%
Where did you go last night?

00:06:44.850 --> 00:06:46.460 line:80%
Did you go to the Library?

00:06:52.610 --> 00:06:53.500 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:06:54.460 --> 00:06:55.340 line:80%
I'm here for Chang.

00:06:56.610 --> 00:06:57.730 line:80%
I asked Xingjia to verify.

00:06:58.610 --> 00:06:59.450 line:80%
This calming powder

00:06:59.850 --> 00:07:01.700 line:80%
was developed by Uncle Lei for Chang.

00:07:01.940 --> 00:07:03.940 line:80%
I don't know
how it ended up in the Library.

00:07:08.210 --> 00:07:09.170 line:80%
I didn't get to deliver

00:07:09.530 --> 00:07:10.610 line:80%
the powder for Ning.

00:07:13.170 --> 00:07:14.610 line:80%
Last night, in the Library,

00:07:15.050 --> 00:07:16.083 line:80%
I accidentally spilled it.

00:07:16.410 --> 00:07:17.250 line:80%
Zhao, last night,

00:07:17.940 --> 00:07:19.140 line:80%
why go to the Library?

00:07:19.186 --> 00:07:20.740 line:80%
To check recipes for a late-night snack.

00:07:21.019 --> 00:07:22.266 line:80%
But I didn't find the right one.

00:07:22.730 --> 00:07:23.570 line:80%
What?

00:07:24.210 --> 00:07:25.416 line:80%
Something lost in the Library?

00:07:25.730 --> 00:07:26.570 line:80%
No.

00:07:26.820 --> 00:07:28.020 line:80%
Just a plaque

00:07:28.460 --> 00:07:29.460 line:80%
fell inexplicably.

00:07:32.090 --> 00:07:32.930 line:80%
In that case,

00:07:33.170 --> 00:07:34.010 line:80%
I'll take my leave.

00:07:35.970 --> 00:07:37.290 line:80%
Yuzhi, goodbye.

00:07:42.460 --> 00:07:43.410 line:80%
I'll move out now.

00:07:43.940 --> 00:07:44.886 line:80%
Find the handbook first.

00:07:48.740 --> 00:07:49.973 line:80%
Yin Dai had only two daughters.

00:07:50.940 --> 00:07:51.780 line:80%
Song Yuzhi's mother,

00:07:51.780 --> 00:07:53.170 line:80%
Lady Qinglian, already passed.

00:07:54.460 --> 00:07:56.460 line:80%
So, his relics should be
with Lady Sulian.

00:07:58.140 --> 00:07:59.393 line:80%
I searched the sect thoroughly

00:08:00.186 --> 00:08:02.170 line:80%
and thought it'd be
in the Library's secret room.

00:08:03.140 --> 00:08:03.980 line:80%
Since it's not there,

00:08:05.650 --> 00:08:07.380 line:80%
it must be in Double Lotus Palace.

00:08:08.940 --> 00:08:10.900 line:80%
Unfortunately, I found nothing
in Treasure Vault.

00:08:12.580 --> 00:08:14.170 line:80%
In such a short time,

00:08:14.340 --> 00:08:16.580 line:80%
you've found out so much.

00:08:20.060 --> 00:08:21.540 line:80%
(Dusk Palace)

00:08:21.540 --> 00:08:22.700 line:80%
(Library)

00:08:23.090 --> 00:08:24.580 line:80%
Have you searched elsewhere?

00:08:25.693 --> 00:08:26.806 line:80%
Have you tried the waterway?

00:08:27.170 --> 00:08:28.010 line:80%
Waterway?

00:08:29.580 --> 00:08:30.610 line:80%
They have many guards.

00:08:32.220 --> 00:08:33.620 line:80%
If I recklessly dive in,

00:08:34.330 --> 00:08:35.500 line:80%
I might alert them.

00:08:42.740 --> 00:08:43.580 line:80%
Mid-Autumn is coming.

00:08:44.620 --> 00:08:45.620 line:80%
There should be

00:08:46.690 --> 00:08:47.740 line:80%
a celebration.

00:08:51.810 --> 00:08:52.650 line:80%
I have an idea.

00:08:52.930 --> 00:08:54.690 line:80%
Go find Lingbo and have another quarrel.

00:08:55.740 --> 00:08:57.020 line:80%
Lighting lanterns for Mid-Autumn

00:08:57.100 --> 00:08:58.930 line:80%
is a century-old tradition here.

00:08:59.106 --> 00:09:00.319 line:80%
With so many people this year,

00:09:00.330 --> 00:09:01.930 line:80%
my mother prepared over 100 lanterns.

00:09:02.330 --> 00:09:03.330 line:80%
It must be lively.

00:09:03.570 --> 00:09:04.930 line:80%
It's just a way

00:09:05.900 --> 00:09:07.050 line:80%
to honor your grandfather

00:09:08.810 --> 00:09:10.620 line:80%
and sing praises of your family.

00:09:10.980 --> 00:09:12.463 line:80%
My grandfather was a hero.

00:09:12.474 --> 00:09:13.380 line:80%
What's wrong with that?

00:09:13.380 --> 00:09:14.810 line:80%
Should we honor your family instead?

00:09:15.410 --> 00:09:16.500 line:80%
Chang Ning, I warn you.

00:09:16.646 --> 00:09:18.245 line:80%
This is a major event of the Six Sects.

00:09:18.410 --> 00:09:19.330 line:80%
Don't write Chang

00:09:19.330 --> 00:09:20.530 line:80%
on the lanterns.

00:09:20.530 --> 00:09:21.500 line:80%
Why not?

00:09:22.380 --> 00:09:24.000 line:80%
Father may not belong to the Six Sects,

00:09:24.260 --> 00:09:25.810 line:80%
but he is a hero.

00:09:25.810 --> 00:09:26.650 line:80%
Ridiculous.

00:09:27.530 --> 00:09:29.620 line:80%
Which hero hides sneakily

00:09:29.930 --> 00:09:31.140 line:80%
and sets traps?

00:09:32.100 --> 00:09:32.940 line:80%
I heard

00:09:33.220 --> 00:09:35.450 line:80%
the turf in Chang Fort was dug up.

00:09:35.980 --> 00:09:37.170 line:80%
What shameful thing

00:09:37.170 --> 00:09:38.690 line:80%
could you be hiding?

00:09:42.140 --> 00:09:42.980 line:80%
Ning,

00:09:43.103 --> 00:09:44.049 line:80%
time to go to Herb Hut.

00:09:51.220 --> 00:09:52.650 line:80%
I'll handle the lanterns.

00:10:07.290 --> 00:10:08.130 line:80%
Just put them here.

00:10:12.450 --> 00:10:13.530 line:80%
A little higher.

00:10:16.780 --> 00:10:17.620 line:80%
Xingjia.

00:10:19.170 --> 00:10:20.380 line:80%
What are you worried about?

00:10:22.220 --> 00:10:24.290 line:80%
Buying for the celebration

00:10:24.570 --> 00:10:26.500 line:80%
and the Patriarch's ceremony

00:10:26.500 --> 00:10:27.570 line:80%
cost a lot.

00:10:27.810 --> 00:10:28.740 line:80%
Money

00:10:28.740 --> 00:10:30.330 line:80%
just flows away,

00:10:30.330 --> 00:10:31.410 line:80%
faster than water.

00:10:32.450 --> 00:10:33.620 line:80%
Managing this is hard.

00:10:35.260 --> 00:10:36.740 line:80%
But Double Lotus Palace

00:10:36.740 --> 00:10:37.650 line:80%
looks splendid.

00:10:38.260 --> 00:10:39.453 line:80%
You don't seem short on money.

00:10:40.780 --> 00:10:41.620 line:80%
Stop thinking.

00:10:41.810 --> 00:10:43.190 line:80%
That is the Yins' private property,

00:10:43.290 --> 00:10:44.330 line:80%
not Qingque Sect's.

00:10:48.530 --> 00:10:49.810 line:80%
Hu paper is light and strong,

00:10:50.290 --> 00:10:52.410 line:80%
the best choice for lanterns,

00:10:53.450 --> 00:10:54.780 line:80%
but expensive.

00:10:55.220 --> 00:10:57.260 line:80%
Lady Yin insists on 100 lanterns.

00:10:57.260 --> 00:10:58.570 line:80%
Another large expense.

00:10:59.220 --> 00:11:01.050 line:80%
Why not use Xuan paper?

00:11:01.500 --> 00:11:03.570 line:80%
Xuan paper costs similar to Hu paper.

00:11:05.170 --> 00:11:07.570 line:80%
That was before.

00:11:07.900 --> 00:11:09.930 line:80%
Because Xuan paper was made
from mulberry bark.

00:11:10.140 --> 00:11:11.260 line:80%
Now, I heard

00:11:11.500 --> 00:11:13.450 line:80%
everyone uses Qingtan for Xuan paper,

00:11:13.900 --> 00:11:15.690 line:80%
so it's much cheaper than Hu paper.

00:11:16.690 --> 00:11:18.620 line:80%
That's perfect.

00:11:19.050 --> 00:11:21.170 line:80%
I'll go to buy more Xuan paper.

00:11:42.580 --> 00:11:44.900 line:80%
(Jiang)

00:11:57.360 --> 00:11:59.470 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle♪

00:11:59.940 --> 00:12:01.800 line:80%
♪And spring is fair♪

00:12:02.410 --> 00:12:04.950 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills♪

00:12:05.700 --> 00:12:08.180 line:80%
(Drinks in Spring)

00:12:08.180 --> 00:12:10.010 line:80%
♪With a shining cup♪

00:12:10.300 --> 00:12:12.300 line:80%
(Everlasting Peace)

00:12:12.330 --> 00:12:13.950 line:80%
Blessings

00:12:13.950 --> 00:12:16.950 line:80%
♪Free to wander♪

00:12:17.620 --> 00:12:19.700 line:80%
(Family Reunion)

00:12:19.700 --> 00:12:24.710 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:12:24.940 --> 00:12:29.160 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:12:29.740 --> 00:12:34.140 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:12:36.810 --> 00:12:38.860 line:80%
So beautiful.

00:12:39.450 --> 00:12:40.980 line:80%
There's more to see later.

00:12:45.980 --> 00:12:49.900 line:80%
(Generation to Generation)

00:12:51.930 --> 00:12:52.810 line:80%
What's that?

00:12:55.450 --> 00:12:56.290 line:80%
It's the Guming Moth.

00:12:56.930 --> 00:12:57.770 line:80%
Be careful.

00:12:57.930 --> 00:12:59.650 line:80%
One bite drives people mad.

00:12:59.900 --> 00:13:01.410 line:80%
(Long Life)

00:13:01.410 --> 00:13:03.780 line:80%
This moth feeds on Qingtan,

00:13:03.930 --> 00:13:05.650 line:80%
living in cool, secluded places.

00:13:06.380 --> 00:13:07.650 line:80%
Why appear suddenly?

00:13:08.740 --> 00:13:09.580 line:80%
Oh, no.

00:13:10.050 --> 00:13:11.690 line:80%
The lantern's paper contains Qingtan.

00:13:13.114 --> 00:13:14.008 line:80%
(Reunion and Harmony)

00:13:14.019 --> 00:13:14.900 line:80%
(Long Life, Longevity)

00:13:32.980 --> 00:13:33.820 line:80%
Ning!

00:13:36.330 --> 00:13:37.500 line:80%
Chang Ning was bitten?

00:13:44.500 --> 00:13:45.860 line:80%
Chang Ning, are you mad?

00:13:46.980 --> 00:13:48.450 line:80%
Those insulting my family

00:13:48.740 --> 00:13:49.650 line:80%
shall die!

00:14:07.900 --> 00:14:09.330 line:80%
Lingbo, run!

00:14:09.570 --> 00:14:10.950 line:80%
Chang's medicine contains Qingtan.

00:14:10.961 --> 00:14:12.290 line:80%
He must've gone mad from the bite.

00:14:13.140 --> 00:14:13.980 line:80%
Run!

00:14:27.530 --> 00:14:28.370 line:80%
Bad news!

00:14:28.410 --> 00:14:29.290 line:80%
Uncle Lei!

00:14:29.290 --> 00:14:30.160 line:80%
Bad news!

00:14:30.330 --> 00:14:31.170 line:80%
Chang Ning,

00:14:32.020 --> 00:14:33.450 line:80%
bitten by the Guming Moth, went mad.

00:14:33.740 --> 00:14:35.530 line:80%
He's shouting to kill Lingbo.

00:14:39.100 --> 00:14:40.050 line:80%
Uncle Lei,

00:14:40.530 --> 00:14:41.370 line:80%
should we intervene?

00:14:41.930 --> 00:14:43.020 line:80%
Everything has a cause.

00:14:43.860 --> 00:14:45.740 line:80%
Don't you understand why Chang Ning

00:14:46.530 --> 00:14:47.450 line:80%
acts against Lingbo?

00:14:48.650 --> 00:14:49.930 line:80%
A little suffering for Lingbo

00:14:50.500 --> 00:14:51.400 line:80%
is not necessarily bad.

00:14:52.170 --> 00:14:53.740 line:80%
But Chang Ning has lost his mind.

00:14:53.780 --> 00:14:54.980 line:80%
Will Lingbo be safe?

00:14:55.020 --> 00:14:56.690 line:80%
Will Chang be severely punished?

00:14:57.410 --> 00:14:58.980 line:80%
Bites from the Guming Moth can cause

00:14:59.620 --> 00:15:00.693 line:80%
hallucinations and madness,

00:15:01.530 --> 00:15:03.020 line:80%
but poison fades quickly.

00:15:03.860 --> 00:15:05.020 line:80%
It won't cause major trouble.

00:15:07.650 --> 00:15:09.050 line:80%
Out of respect for Lord Yin,

00:15:09.620 --> 00:15:11.620 line:80%
Master never punishes Lingbo properly

00:15:11.860 --> 00:15:13.650 line:80%
for her mistakes.

00:15:14.450 --> 00:15:15.290 line:80%
Similarly,

00:15:15.650 --> 00:15:17.330 line:80%
for the late Mr. Chang,

00:15:17.650 --> 00:15:19.220 line:80%
even if Chang Ning caused a mess,

00:15:19.380 --> 00:15:20.980 line:80%
Lord Qi won't severely punish

00:15:21.100 --> 00:15:22.380 line:80%
the orphan of the Chang family.

00:15:34.930 --> 00:15:35.770 line:80%
Uncle Lei,

00:15:35.900 --> 00:15:37.140 line:80%
the blessing charms are copied.

00:15:37.290 --> 00:15:38.330 line:80%
I'll leave first.

00:15:45.980 --> 00:15:47.330 line:80%
Since you've understood,

00:15:48.100 --> 00:15:49.020 line:80%
why still go?

00:15:51.570 --> 00:15:52.530 line:80%
Lady Yin is still there.

00:15:56.690 --> 00:15:57.530 line:80%
Stop him!

00:15:57.900 --> 00:15:58.860 line:80%
Stop him now!

00:16:43.410 --> 00:16:44.250 line:80%
Chang Ning!

00:16:49.530 --> 00:16:50.370 line:80%
Enough!

00:16:55.290 --> 00:16:56.130 line:80%
Zhao!

00:17:29.890 --> 00:17:31.020 line:80%
Have you had enough madness?

00:17:38.780 --> 00:17:39.620 line:80%
Come back with me.

00:17:55.420 --> 00:17:56.260 line:80%
What do you want?

00:18:08.500 --> 00:18:09.780 line:80%
Help!

00:18:10.880 --> 00:18:11.720 line:80%
Help!

00:18:12.370 --> 00:18:13.210 line:80%
Help!

00:18:14.610 --> 00:18:15.610 line:80%
Help!

00:18:18.130 --> 00:18:19.260 line:80%
Yuzhi!

00:18:22.700 --> 00:18:23.940 line:80%
Someone wants to kill me!

00:18:24.500 --> 00:18:25.340 line:80%
It's him!

00:18:26.180 --> 00:18:27.370 line:80%
- Ning.
- It's him!

00:18:27.420 --> 00:18:28.940 line:80%
He tried to kill me!

00:18:30.130 --> 00:18:30.970 line:80%
Lady Yin,

00:18:31.980 --> 00:18:33.660 line:80%
Ning's been missing his family,

00:18:34.020 --> 00:18:34.946 line:80%
so he's lost his mind.

00:18:35.639 --> 00:18:36.833 line:80%
I'll take him back to recover.

00:18:37.180 --> 00:18:38.220 line:80%
He'll apologize later.

00:18:39.370 --> 00:18:40.210 line:80%
Recovery comes first.

00:18:48.890 --> 00:18:50.260 line:80%
They just left like that?

00:18:53.740 --> 00:18:54.580 line:80%
Where is Master?

00:18:56.420 --> 00:18:58.460 line:80%
(No Regrets)

00:19:00.500 --> 00:19:03.940 line:80%
(No Regrets)

00:19:20.090 --> 00:19:20.930 line:80%
Xiaolan,

00:19:22.570 --> 00:19:23.410 line:80%
thank you this time.

00:19:24.220 --> 00:19:25.260 line:80%
Zhao, you're welcome.

00:19:25.570 --> 00:19:26.570 line:80%
I didn't do much.

00:19:27.610 --> 00:19:28.903 line:80%
There was no one by the lakeside.

00:19:29.180 --> 00:19:30.500 line:80%
How did you fall into the water?

00:19:34.090 --> 00:19:34.930 line:80%
I know

00:19:34.980 --> 00:19:35.850 line:80%
you wanted to help us.

00:19:36.830 --> 00:19:37.670 line:80%
I...

00:19:37.700 --> 00:19:39.420 line:80%
I don't know what happened.

00:19:39.740 --> 00:19:41.570 line:80%
I just felt that Nanny Mao was fierce;

00:19:41.740 --> 00:19:43.040 line:80%
I didn't want her to trouble you.

00:19:45.220 --> 00:19:46.060 line:80%
Zhao,

00:19:47.050 --> 00:19:48.420 line:80%
Mr. Chang is still injured.

00:19:48.660 --> 00:19:49.660 line:80%
Take him back now.

00:19:49.850 --> 00:19:50.690 line:80%
I'll go first.

00:20:10.460 --> 00:20:11.660 line:80%
Siqi Sect is useless,

00:20:12.660 --> 00:20:14.740 line:80%
but Yang Heying has a good daughter.

00:20:16.610 --> 00:20:17.460 line:80%
Sorry

00:20:18.700 --> 00:20:19.540 line:80%
about that.

00:20:20.890 --> 00:20:22.180 line:80%
Were you worried

00:20:22.500 --> 00:20:24.020 line:80%
that I'd kill Qi Lingbo?

00:20:25.130 --> 00:20:25.970 line:80%
Would you?

00:21:34.740 --> 00:21:36.330 line:80%
So many martial arts secrets.

00:21:37.090 --> 00:21:38.850 line:80%
Including Peiqiong Manor's swordsmanship

00:21:39.090 --> 00:21:40.290 line:80%
and our mindful ways.

00:21:40.530 --> 00:21:42.130 line:80%
Isn't he already the Lord?

00:21:42.660 --> 00:21:45.420 line:80%
Why collect martial secrets
from all sects?

00:21:46.500 --> 00:21:48.180 line:80%
Naturally, to unify Jianghu

00:21:48.610 --> 00:21:49.500 line:80%
for generations.

00:21:53.980 --> 00:21:54.966 line:80%
The fire is almost out.

00:21:55.220 --> 00:21:56.060 line:80%
I'll get it.

00:21:57.570 --> 00:21:58.410 line:80%
Let me.

00:22:38.290 --> 00:22:39.660 line:80%
Control movement.

00:22:39.660 --> 00:22:40.850 line:80%
Let the soul guard the body.

00:22:41.035 --> 00:22:42.549 line:80%
Change between fullness and emptiness.

00:22:42.560 --> 00:22:43.220 line:80%
Try to reverse.

00:22:43.220 --> 00:22:44.610 line:80%
This is the Disintegration.

00:22:45.260 --> 00:22:46.500 line:80%
It can stimulate all meridians

00:22:47.050 --> 00:22:47.980 line:80%
and boost power tenfold.

00:22:48.700 --> 00:22:50.260 line:80%
Truly extraordinary.

00:22:56.940 --> 00:22:58.610 line:80%
As you said,

00:22:58.740 --> 00:22:59.810 line:80%
Chang Ning

00:22:59.810 --> 00:23:01.530 line:80%
is crazy.

00:23:02.020 --> 00:23:04.260 line:80%
He even attacked Cai Zhao.

00:23:04.940 --> 00:23:05.923 line:80%
With Zhao's skill,

00:23:06.141 --> 00:23:07.903 line:80%
how could she fall
into the water so easily?

00:23:17.570 --> 00:23:18.410 line:80%
Lady Yin,

00:23:19.420 --> 00:23:20.653 line:80%
is the item hidden in the water

00:23:21.050 --> 00:23:22.330 line:80%
the one I brought as a child?

00:23:22.330 --> 00:23:23.170 line:80%
Exactly.

00:23:23.500 --> 00:23:25.050 line:80%
It's your grandfather's handbook,

00:23:25.500 --> 00:23:27.330 line:80%
recording the supreme martial arts

00:23:27.370 --> 00:23:29.220 line:80%
and martial arts secrets that he spent

00:23:29.290 --> 00:23:30.276 line:80%
half his life collecting.

00:23:30.850 --> 00:23:32.530 line:80%
But he was the former lord.

00:23:32.980 --> 00:23:34.740 line:80%
Shouldn't his handbook
be handed to Master?

00:23:35.980 --> 00:23:37.370 line:80%
Your grandfather's belongings

00:23:37.530 --> 00:23:39.090 line:80%
stay with the Yin descendants.

00:23:39.850 --> 00:23:41.130 line:80%
Your mother and I preserved them

00:23:41.700 --> 00:23:42.540 line:80%
for you.

00:23:43.850 --> 00:23:45.020 line:80%
But it's gotten this far.

00:23:46.420 --> 00:23:47.893 line:80%
We can no longer hide it from Master.

00:23:52.290 --> 00:23:53.740 line:80%
During the battle,

00:23:54.330 --> 00:23:56.420 line:80%
the Six Sects suffered heavy casualties.

00:23:57.570 --> 00:23:59.740 line:80%
I'm old and injured,

00:23:59.850 --> 00:24:01.050 line:80%
powerless to oppose the enemy.

00:24:01.940 --> 00:24:03.850 line:80%
Seeing the demons run rampant,

00:24:04.050 --> 00:24:05.460 line:80%
killing even more,

00:24:06.700 --> 00:24:08.180 line:80%
Pingshu of Luoying Valley

00:24:08.180 --> 00:24:10.330 line:80%
volunteered to slay Nie.

00:24:11.020 --> 00:24:13.610 line:80%
I had no choice but to teach her
our forbidden secret:

00:24:13.780 --> 00:24:16.890 line:80%
Disintegration.

00:24:28.220 --> 00:24:30.540 line:80%
(Young Cai Zhao, Luoying Valley)

00:24:36.980 --> 00:24:38.980 line:80%
(Disintegration)

00:25:39.420 --> 00:25:40.740 line:80%
If you wish to learn martial arts,

00:25:41.220 --> 00:25:42.780 line:80%
I'll spare no effort to teach you.

00:25:43.500 --> 00:25:45.180 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)
Why go to such lengths?

00:25:45.660 --> 00:25:46.500 line:80%
Master,

00:25:47.260 --> 00:25:48.890 line:80%
did you know my aunt practiced

00:25:49.090 --> 00:25:49.940 line:80%
the Disintegration?

00:25:51.780 --> 00:25:52.620 line:80%
If I had known,

00:25:54.290 --> 00:25:55.980 line:80%
I would've risked
everything to stop her.

00:25:56.700 --> 00:25:58.660 line:80%
I only discovered it
while treating her injuries,

00:25:59.780 --> 00:26:00.890 line:80%
but it was too late.

00:26:01.500 --> 00:26:02.500 line:80%
The Disintegration

00:26:03.180 --> 00:26:04.850 line:80%
is a secret of Qingque lords.

00:26:05.370 --> 00:26:07.290 line:80%
My aunt is not your direct disciple,

00:26:07.301 --> 00:26:08.700 line:80%
so how could it be for her to learn?

00:26:08.700 --> 00:26:10.330 line:80%
I asked Lord Yin about this.

00:26:10.700 --> 00:26:12.460 line:80%
He said he was severely injured,

00:26:12.780 --> 00:26:14.653 line:80%
and his disciples were
either dead or invalid,

00:26:14.940 --> 00:26:16.290 line:80%
unable to resist the demons.

00:26:16.850 --> 00:26:18.460 line:80%
Pingshu volunteered

00:26:18.850 --> 00:26:20.020 line:80%
for the greater good.

00:26:20.810 --> 00:26:21.869 line:80%
He had no choice but to...

00:26:22.090 --> 00:26:23.020 line:80%
What?

00:26:24.260 --> 00:26:26.050 line:80%
To sacrifice my aunt
for the greater good?

00:26:33.330 --> 00:26:34.180 line:80%
I also

00:26:35.260 --> 00:26:36.290 line:80%
resented Master for this,

00:26:37.370 --> 00:26:38.220 line:80%
but soon after,

00:26:39.180 --> 00:26:40.530 line:80%
he was killed by the demon sect.

00:26:42.330 --> 00:26:43.170 line:80%
Zhao,

00:26:43.756 --> 00:26:45.056 line:80%
the previous generation's affairs

00:26:45.530 --> 00:26:47.660 line:80%
are for the previous generation
to bear and resolve.

00:26:48.370 --> 00:26:49.460 line:80%
You need not interfere.

00:26:51.460 --> 00:26:52.740 line:80%
No one is allowed

00:26:53.940 --> 00:26:55.530 line:80%
to practice this sinister move again.

00:26:59.340 --> 00:27:00.939 line:80%
The Founder's death anniversary
is near.

00:27:01.050 --> 00:27:02.420 line:80%
Master already exerts much effort.

00:27:02.810 --> 00:27:03.890 line:80%
Stop causing trouble.

00:27:07.660 --> 00:27:08.740 line:80%
The deceased are gone.

00:27:09.660 --> 00:27:10.940 line:80%
Master will handle the rest.

00:27:11.700 --> 00:27:12.660 line:80%
You must let go.

00:27:12.940 --> 00:27:14.260 line:80%
Let go?

00:27:15.183 --> 00:27:17.262 line:80%
Isn't this the consistent approach
of the Six Sects?

00:27:18.090 --> 00:27:20.330 line:80%
Is that how you see the Six Sects?

00:27:22.420 --> 00:27:23.420 line:80%
Isn't he right?

00:27:24.610 --> 00:27:25.450 line:80%
An unavoidable choice

00:27:25.890 --> 00:27:27.570 line:80%
shouldn't cost others' lives.

00:27:28.370 --> 00:27:29.570 line:80%
You're noble and upright,

00:27:29.660 --> 00:27:30.780 line:80%
act with integrity,

00:27:30.980 --> 00:27:32.530 line:80%
yet can let go easily.

00:27:32.890 --> 00:27:34.020 line:80%
I really admire that.

00:27:35.220 --> 00:27:36.200 line:80%
I don't intend to argue.

00:27:36.570 --> 00:27:38.220 line:80%
If you ever need me

00:27:38.220 --> 00:27:39.180 line:80%
for difficulties,

00:27:39.610 --> 00:27:40.700 line:80%
I won't refuse.

00:27:44.330 --> 00:27:45.170 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:27:45.460 --> 00:27:46.980 line:80%
Chang Ning ruined the lantern festival

00:27:46.980 --> 00:27:47.872 line:80%
and injured Fengchi,

00:27:47.883 --> 00:27:49.050 line:80%
yet Father didn't punish him.

00:27:49.090 --> 00:27:50.220 line:80%
Does that mean it's over?

00:27:55.700 --> 00:27:56.540 line:80%
Originally,

00:27:56.780 --> 00:27:57.873 line:80%
he should've been punished,

00:27:58.020 --> 00:28:00.180 line:80%
but Yuzhi felt Ning had no choice,

00:28:00.570 --> 00:28:02.090 line:80%
so he pleaded for him.

00:28:02.530 --> 00:28:03.660 line:80%
Then Master calmed down.

00:28:03.790 --> 00:28:04.640 line:80%
Is that right,

00:28:04.660 --> 00:28:05.500 line:80%
Yuzhi?

00:28:06.260 --> 00:28:07.290 line:80%
He had no choice

00:28:07.290 --> 00:28:08.530 line:80%
but bully me?

00:28:08.890 --> 00:28:11.500 line:80%
Yuzhi just values reason more.

00:28:13.090 --> 00:28:14.130 line:80%
I'm grateful,

00:28:14.260 --> 00:28:16.130 line:80%
so I prepared sweet lotus congee.

00:28:16.460 --> 00:28:18.220 line:80%
My cooking is exceptional.

00:28:18.740 --> 00:28:19.850 line:80%
Yuzhi, why not come back

00:28:19.850 --> 00:28:20.700 line:80%
with us to try it?

00:28:21.180 --> 00:28:22.020 line:80%
Let's go.

00:28:22.220 --> 00:28:23.570 line:80%
What are you doing, Cai Zhao?

00:28:24.980 --> 00:28:27.050 line:80%
It's one thing to be involved
with Chang Ning.

00:28:27.050 --> 00:28:28.050 line:80%
Why drag my cousin?

00:28:30.020 --> 00:28:31.020 line:80%
I'll take you back first.

00:28:38.890 --> 00:28:39.780 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:28:42.780 --> 00:28:43.700 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:28:44.050 --> 00:28:45.220 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:28:45.810 --> 00:28:47.370 line:80%
why always protect Cai Zhao?

00:28:47.740 --> 00:28:49.000 line:80%
She's only been here a few days.

00:28:49.220 --> 00:28:51.610 line:80%
We grew up together for over ten years.

00:28:51.940 --> 00:28:53.660 line:80%
Today's matter has nothing
to do with Zhao.

00:28:54.220 --> 00:28:55.850 line:80%
Don't trouble her again.

00:28:57.050 --> 00:28:58.700 line:80%
We owe Zhao anyway.

00:28:59.330 --> 00:29:00.220 line:80%
Owe her what?

00:29:01.220 --> 00:29:02.260 line:80%
You keep calling her Zhao.

00:29:02.260 --> 00:29:03.370 line:80%
How intimate.

00:29:03.740 --> 00:29:05.130 line:80%
She also has congee for you.

00:29:10.780 --> 00:29:11.890 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:29:12.180 --> 00:29:13.290 line:80%
do you like her?

00:29:13.290 --> 00:29:14.130 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:29:15.220 --> 00:29:16.460 line:80%
Lingbo, you're no child.

00:29:16.810 --> 00:29:17.940 line:80%
You must mind limits.

00:29:20.940 --> 00:29:22.330 line:80%
Cai Zhao just held your hand.

00:29:22.330 --> 00:29:23.420 line:80%
Did she mind her limits?

00:29:23.980 --> 00:29:25.130 line:80%
Knowing about our betrothal,

00:29:25.141 --> 00:29:26.040 line:80%
she openly provoked me.

00:29:26.090 --> 00:29:26.940 line:80%
How shameless.

00:29:26.940 --> 00:29:27.780 line:80%
I'll say it again.

00:29:28.050 --> 00:29:29.330 line:80%
Cai Zhao is Master's disciple,

00:29:29.740 --> 00:29:30.740 line:80%
our junior sister.

00:29:31.260 --> 00:29:33.130 line:80%
If you continue slandering
and causing trouble,

00:29:33.130 --> 00:29:34.530 line:80%
forget our relationship.

00:29:36.090 --> 00:29:36.980 line:80%
Yuzhi!

00:29:47.130 --> 00:29:48.530 line:80%
(Control movement.)

00:29:48.530 --> 00:29:49.700 line:80%
(Let the soul guard the body.)

00:29:50.030 --> 00:29:51.600 line:80%
(Change between fullness and emptiness.)

00:29:51.611 --> 00:29:52.420 line:80%
(Try to reverse.)

00:29:54.700 --> 00:29:55.540 line:80%
Stop it.

00:29:55.830 --> 00:29:56.680 line:80%
Why?

00:29:56.700 --> 00:29:57.780 line:80%
You know how dangerous

00:29:58.980 --> 00:30:00.090 line:80%
this move is.

00:30:00.563 --> 00:30:02.050 line:80%
Those who practice it die in the end.

00:30:02.060 --> 00:30:02.910 line:80%
It's not worth it.

00:30:02.940 --> 00:30:04.460 line:80%
My life is for revenge.

00:30:05.290 --> 00:30:07.020 line:80%
If revenge costs my life, so be it.

00:30:07.980 --> 00:30:09.810 line:80%
When Ms. Cai went to meet Nie Hengcheng,

00:30:10.460 --> 00:30:11.700 line:80%
she knew she'd die.

00:30:22.130 --> 00:30:23.780 line:80%
Those who practice the Disintegration

00:30:25.610 --> 00:30:27.130 line:80%
will have their meridians destroyed

00:30:27.780 --> 00:30:28.940 line:80%
and organs collapse.

00:30:31.260 --> 00:30:32.420 line:80%
Do you know that pain?

00:30:36.370 --> 00:30:38.660 line:80%
She had suffered for 13 years.

00:30:41.570 --> 00:30:42.850 line:80%
She was only 30,

00:30:43.530 --> 00:30:44.660 line:80%
younger than Yin Sulian,

00:30:47.660 --> 00:30:49.330 line:80%
and had wasted away.

00:30:52.330 --> 00:30:53.370 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng is dead;

00:30:54.330 --> 00:30:55.420 line:80%
Yin Dai is dead.

00:30:56.850 --> 00:30:58.420 line:80%
I don't know who to hate now.

00:31:02.370 --> 00:31:03.290 line:80%
No matter who you are,

00:31:04.290 --> 00:31:05.610 line:80%
no matter your purpose,

00:31:06.700 --> 00:31:08.780 line:80%
you are forbidden to practice it.

00:31:09.780 --> 00:31:10.620 line:80%
As I said,

00:31:11.220 --> 00:31:12.220 line:80%
I'll protect you.

00:31:14.420 --> 00:31:16.090 line:80%
I'll never let you

00:31:16.370 --> 00:31:18.180 line:80%
die like my aunt.

00:31:19.980 --> 00:31:20.820 line:80%
Promise me.

00:31:25.370 --> 00:31:26.210 line:80%
Okay.

00:31:26.610 --> 00:31:27.450 line:80%
Swear.

00:31:28.260 --> 00:31:29.290 line:80%
I swear

00:31:31.570 --> 00:31:33.570 line:80%
never to practice the Disintegration.

00:32:00.610 --> 00:32:01.450 line:80%
Chang Ning.

00:32:07.940 --> 00:32:08.780 line:80%
I'm hungry.

00:32:08.890 --> 00:32:09.810 line:80%
I want some wonton.

00:32:17.530 --> 00:32:20.290 line:80%
Your disciple stole
my father's handbook.

00:32:21.370 --> 00:32:22.890 line:80%
It's been destroyed.

00:32:23.260 --> 00:32:25.660 line:80%
Let this matter end here.

00:32:26.050 --> 00:32:27.980 line:80%
You destroyed
my father's relics at will.

00:32:28.420 --> 00:32:29.700 line:80%
What do you take me for?

00:32:29.980 --> 00:32:31.460 line:80%
Keeping it would have been a hazard.

00:32:33.050 --> 00:32:33.890 line:80%
Do you want

00:32:35.050 --> 00:32:37.460 line:80%
the world to know

00:32:38.530 --> 00:32:40.180 line:80%
what your father did?

00:32:41.570 --> 00:32:42.876 line:80%
The martial arts knowledge inside

00:32:43.700 --> 00:32:45.370 line:80%
is all his life's work,

00:32:46.460 --> 00:32:47.660 line:80%
yet you've destroyed it?

00:32:48.460 --> 00:32:49.810 line:80%
What's the point of keeping it?

00:32:50.460 --> 00:32:52.370 line:80%
Lingbo is not suited for martial arts.

00:32:52.370 --> 00:32:53.370 line:80%
We both know that.

00:32:53.530 --> 00:32:54.460 line:80%
We have Yuzhi.

00:32:55.570 --> 00:32:57.660 line:80%
He'll inherit the sect eventually.

00:32:58.050 --> 00:32:59.180 line:80%
Once they marry,

00:32:59.180 --> 00:33:00.020 line:80%
we'll be family.

00:33:00.180 --> 00:33:01.420 line:80%
We could've given it to him.

00:33:02.180 --> 00:33:03.850 line:80%
If Lingbo continues to be so headstrong,

00:33:04.420 --> 00:33:05.570 line:80%
I fear Yuzhi

00:33:06.050 --> 00:33:08.130 line:80%
might not want to fulfill the betrothal.

00:33:08.890 --> 00:33:09.740 line:80%
He will,

00:33:10.740 --> 00:33:11.580 line:80%
and he won't dare,

00:33:12.980 --> 00:33:13.820 line:80%
unless

00:33:15.570 --> 00:33:17.260 line:80%
he doesn't want to be the future lord.

00:33:52.290 --> 00:33:53.130 line:80%
You made it?

00:33:53.980 --> 00:33:54.980 line:80%
Homemade cooking.

00:33:55.180 --> 00:33:56.020 line:80%
I wonder

00:33:56.020 --> 00:33:57.460 line:80%
if you'll like it.

00:34:19.660 --> 00:34:20.810 line:80%
It's just a bowl of wonton.

00:34:21.580 --> 00:34:22.780 line:80%
No need to be so touched.

00:34:23.580 --> 00:34:24.620 line:80%
This flavor

00:34:27.260 --> 00:34:28.970 line:80%
is exactly like my aunt's.

00:34:34.566 --> 00:34:36.066 line:80%
I've thought about it for three years.

00:34:37.260 --> 00:34:38.100 line:80%
Ning,

00:34:40.580 --> 00:34:41.420 line:80%
thank you.

00:35:09.450 --> 00:35:10.290 line:80%
Is there more?

00:35:10.370 --> 00:35:11.660 line:80%
If you like it,

00:35:12.220 --> 00:35:13.410 line:80%
I'll make more

00:35:13.970 --> 00:35:14.810 line:80%
when Han wakes up.

00:35:16.010 --> 00:35:16.850 line:80%
Wonderful.

00:35:18.580 --> 00:35:19.420 line:80%
By the way,

00:35:19.490 --> 00:35:20.540 line:80%
you swore yesterday.

00:35:20.890 --> 00:35:21.740 line:80%
No backing out.

00:35:23.330 --> 00:35:24.170 line:80%
Got it.

00:35:24.410 --> 00:35:25.780 line:80%
Your cooking is so good.

00:35:25.930 --> 00:35:27.100 line:80%
Why not open a diner

00:35:27.620 --> 00:35:28.460 line:80%
in Luoying Valley?

00:35:28.780 --> 00:35:29.689 line:80%
I'll be the shopkeeper;

00:35:29.700 --> 00:35:30.620 line:80%
you handle the kitchen.

00:35:30.850 --> 00:35:32.060 line:80%
We'll have the place

00:35:32.330 --> 00:35:33.330 line:80%
at the street's end,

00:35:33.660 --> 00:35:35.700 line:80%
so when people stroll from head to tail

00:35:35.890 --> 00:35:36.730 line:80%
and get hungry,

00:35:37.140 --> 00:35:38.486 line:80%
they'll come for a bowl of wonton,

00:35:38.580 --> 00:35:39.700 line:80%
leaving a lasting taste.

00:35:40.060 --> 00:35:40.900 line:80%
Perfect.

00:35:42.330 --> 00:35:43.170 line:80%
Chang Ning.

00:35:47.100 --> 00:35:48.850 line:80%
Why are you two here?

00:35:49.260 --> 00:35:50.780 line:80%
About the Mid-Autumn incident,

00:35:50.810 --> 00:35:52.330 line:80%
Master said not to pursue it further.

00:35:52.620 --> 00:35:54.010 line:80%
That night, my skills were inferior.

00:35:54.140 --> 00:35:55.206 line:80%
I have nothing more to say.

00:35:56.100 --> 00:35:57.410 line:80%
But now, it's not about that.

00:35:57.850 --> 00:35:58.690 line:80%
Chang,

00:35:59.100 --> 00:36:00.810 line:80%
Master orders you to go
to Dusk Palace now.

00:36:08.780 --> 00:36:10.810 line:80%
While searching for clues,

00:36:10.930 --> 00:36:12.100 line:80%
I unexpectedly learned

00:36:12.290 --> 00:36:14.660 line:80%
the Changs had an old steward
surnamed Jiang.

00:36:15.850 --> 00:36:16.780 line:80%
Five years ago,

00:36:17.140 --> 00:36:19.450 line:80%
the steward retired to his hometown

00:36:19.450 --> 00:36:20.890 line:80%
and took a boy with him.

00:36:21.290 --> 00:36:22.490 line:80%
After much investigation,

00:36:22.620 --> 00:36:24.660 line:80%
at Steward Jiang's grave,

00:36:24.850 --> 00:36:25.850 line:80%
I found Mr. Jiang,

00:36:25.850 --> 00:36:28.010 line:80%
who resembles the late Mr. Chang,

00:36:28.140 --> 00:36:29.100 line:80%
or rather,

00:36:29.890 --> 00:36:31.410 line:80%
the real Chang Ning.

00:36:43.960 --> 00:36:54.620 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:37:13.380 --> 00:37:17.790 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:37:18.355 --> 00:37:22.970 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:37:23.310 --> 00:37:27.875 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:37:28.400 --> 00:37:32.700 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:37:35.645 --> 00:37:40.345 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:37:40.870 --> 00:37:45.160 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:37:45.820 --> 00:37:49.850 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:37:50.165 --> 00:37:55.290 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:37:55.865 --> 00:38:00.675 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:00.890 --> 00:38:05.060 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:38:05.785 --> 00:38:09.720 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:38:10.220 --> 00:38:15.495 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

